    "During these same years she lectured as an Instructor at the City University of New York in 1973 and at Columbia University in 1975.": [],
    "She joined the New School for Social Research in 1986.": [],
    "Ashton received a National Endowment for the Humanities grant in 1980.": [],
    "Her 1983 personal portrait of Mark Rothko, <em>About Rothko</em>, remains a revealing work on the artist.": [],
